-- TelePoint database upload — image links (part 1 of 4)
-- Sets the ibb DIRECT image links (<img src> = https://i.ibb.co/.../file.jpg)
-- on existing customers, matched by IMEI. The portal's ibbDirect() helper
-- passes i.ibb.co links through unchanged, so the photos actually render —
-- unlike the ibb.co page (href) links, which it mangles into broken URLs.
--
-- Re-runnable: UPDATE ... WHERE imei no-ops for any IMEI not present, and
-- only the listed image columns are touched (other data is untouched).
-- Source: EMI_COMPLETE + Register_book. Statements in this part: 500.
-- Apply parts in order (1..4) in the Supabase SQL editor.

BEGIN;

